# ── Runtime scan artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Written by the scanners at runtime (into data/) and regenerated on every scan.
# They hold real tenant data (user lists, role assignments, resource inventory,
# costs), so they are deliberately NOT version-controlled. data/.gitkeep keeps
# the directory present on a fresh clone.
data/*.json
*-scan-results.json
*-scan-progress.json
scan-results.json
scan-progress.json

# ── Local-only Claude Code settings ──────────────────────────────────────
# launch.json IS tracked (shared preview config); local permission overrides
# are per-machine.
.claude/settings.local.json

# ── Misc ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
text.txt
.DS_Store
